{"tid":893711,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"還我舊時財經台","createTime":"2018-11-08T00:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T23:33:51.000Z","uid":49083,"like":115,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d614052fa5282a20b6790b3d2a4ac907887b8133","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:14:52.000Z","msg":"唔知從幾時開始，財經台日日講物業<br />\n都唔緊要，錢丫嗎，但又唔係咩深入分析，日日夜夜互屌買樓傻定唔傻，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一單樓市成交開一個post</span>，係唔係真係有需要？<br />\n<br />\n正正經經講期股匯金果班又厭世又唔出post，有實力果班又頂唔順唔再上黎，最後淨番班有樓好無樓好但都係無知既日日罵戰，挑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f3911a436f770d38b16c0fad71f8627e3c563a","tid":893711,"uid":134182,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"應該開返個地產台"},{"pid":"80d4a5f4a7b01ebc4ecf413bce04182b014d69e7","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"40f3911a436f770d38b16c0fad71f8627e3c563a","tid":893711,"uid":134182,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"應該開返個地產台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:17:23.000Z","msg":"肉酸過波台同時事台了"},{"pid":"233da584f559d540f43501128f5a05197cd0553e","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:22:58.000Z","msg":"以前施政報告都正經討論十幾版，唔理啱唔啱聽，都叫各種聲音都真係有觀點有理據。<br />\n<br />\n依家除左嬉笑怒罵咩內容都無。<br />\n<br />\n就好似外面D 報價post咁，屌，上個報紙網都睇到喇，洗唔洗就咁搬過黎開post？<br />\n正經post就比人搞到秒沈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d74ebbfa165cb376d8a12793ff60eb9899bdbac","tid":893711,"uid":169008,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"買樓果班人 成日係到屌來屌去<br />\n供多左又唔係你到攞<br />\n供少左又唔會落你袋<br />\n關你撚事咩<br />\n<br />\n供樓果班又係垃撚圾 <br />\n買左自住咪算囉 洗撚理人點理咩<br />\n<br />\n就係班騎呢怪狗咬狗骨 <br />\n搞到財經台污煙瘴氣<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c31712f1c6eeb01150a14d780d78e879a54135","tid":893711,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:31:40.000Z","msg":"淨返班垃圾膠人 日日出燈post"},{"pid":"b2cfecab303740bf9b792dd77e8e61d564c09443","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d74ebbfa165cb376d8a12793ff60eb9899bdbac","tid":893711,"uid":169008,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"買樓果班人 成日係到屌來屌去<br />\n供多左又唔係你到攞<br />\n供少左又唔會落你袋<br />\n關你撚事咩<br />\n<br />\n供樓果班又係垃撚圾 <br />\n買左自住咪算囉 洗撚理人點理咩<br />\n<br />\n就係班騎呢怪狗咬狗骨 <br />\n搞到財經台污煙瘴氣<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"根本佢地觀點唔會磨合，不停互屌<br />\n講到底係有樓又輸唔起，無樓又輸唔起<br />\n各自將生活壓力唔過慮咁羅上財經台呢個本身高手雲集既地方<br />\n<br />\n好喇，無曬勁人，真係想學下野果班無人教"},{"pid":"e981f49e16ae525fcd39b9cbbe49d97da5e6734f","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:36:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝修關財經撚事咩</span>"},{"pid":"ee7c07dca2d39a48c792781556299210043bb59e","tid":893711,"uid":163207,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e981f49e16ae525fcd39b9cbbe49d97da5e6734f","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:36:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝修關財經撚事咩</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"低置仔樓價跌無嘢講要講裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ee66e0ccabc37d6272349416e724af14e2c90d","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T00:47:12.000Z","msg":"1) 無視無內容樓post，不入，不看<br />\n2) 討論帶有有理有據觀點<br />\n3) 減少使用gogogo 等垃圾回覆<br />\n4) 不出報價post<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4faaab5088c25171bcbc33a1bbd9fd0a753d537","tid":893711,"uid":49083,"like":10,"dislike":0,